        <abstract> 
<p>Messrs Clowes will make CD’s corrections and adjust index of <hi rend="italic">Cross and self-fertilisation</hi>. Of this work only 1500 copies have been printed. Edition is sold out and account is enclosed.</p>  
<p>Of 500 copies of <hi rend="italic">Climbing plants</hi> [2d ed.] printed in June 1876, 450 were still unsold as of June 1877.</p> 
